sequenceDiagram
    participant App as 应用
    participant KMS as KMS 服务
    participant KEK as KEK Provider
    participant RNG as 随机数源

    Note over App,KMS: 生成数据密钥 (GenerateDataKey)

    App->>KMS: POST /keys/{id}/datakey
    activate KMS
    KMS->>KEK: unwrap_key(key_id, version)
    activate KEK
    KEK-->>KMS: 明文 KEK (16 bytes)
    deactivate KEK
    KMS->>RNG: 生成 32 字节 DEK
    activate RNG
    RNG-->>KMS: 随机 DEK
    deactivate RNG
    KMS->>KMS: SM4-GCM 加密 DEK<br/>key=KEK, aad="key_id:version"
    KMS-->>App: 密文 DEK (nonce || ct || tag)
    deactivate KMS

    Note over App,KMS: 使用 DEK 加密数据

    App->>App: SM4-GCM 加密明文<br/>key=DEK, aad=上下文
    App-->>用户: 密文 + 密文 DEK

    Note over App,KMS: 解密数据

    App->>KMS: POST /keys/{id}/decrypt<br/>{密文 DEK, key_id, version}
    activate KMS
    KMS->>KEK: unwrap_key(key_id, version)
    activate KEK
    KEK-->>KMS: 明文 KEK
    deactivate KEK
    KMS->>KMS: SM4-GCM 解密 DEK<br/>key=KEK
    KMS-->>App: 明文 DEK
    deactivate KMS
    App->>App: SM4-GCM 解密密文<br/>key=DEK
    App-->>用户: 明文
